item.title: Journal 1: COVID and Liminality
item.description: Alrighty then, I guess it’s journal time! But first, I do realize that it’s been a bit since my first post but it’s not because I forgot about this or anything. It’s just that there are so many things in my life that are competing for my limited attention, and things that require actual work and effort (like writing stuff) always seem to be left out. Now that my excuse is out of the way, time for the real stuff.
